Eksik Olan Kritik Şeyler
1. Folder Architecture Eksik

Şu an Claude kendi kafasına göre folder structure üretir.

Bu ileride kaosa dönüşür.

Mutlaka ekle:

## Project Structure Rules

src/
  app/
  pages/
  modules/
  components/
  features/
  store/
  hooks/
  services/
  lib/
  types/
  i18n/
  assets/

- Shared UI components go into `components/`
- Domain-specific logic goes into `features/`
- Business logic must never live inside UI components
- API/Web APIs go into `services/`
- Reusable hooks go into `hooks/`

Bu çok önemli.

2. Data Model Kuralları Eksik

Şu an “types.ts oluştur” demişsin ama entity architecture yok.

Claude ileride inconsistent model üretir.

Eklenmeli:

## Data Modeling Rules

- Every entity must have:
  - `id`
  - `createdAt`
  - `updatedAt`

- IDs must use UUID format.

- Avoid deeply nested objects.
- Prefer normalized data structures.
- Use discriminated unions for exam task types.
3. Component Rules Eksik

Bu büyük eksik.

Yoksa Claude:

700 satırlık component
inline logic
prop drilling
duplicate state

üretir.

Eklenmeli:

## Component Architecture Rules

- Components must be under 200 lines whenever possible.
- Separate container and presentational components.
- Avoid prop drilling beyond 2 levels.
- Extract reusable logic into hooks.
- Heavy computations must use memoization.
- Use lazy loading for large modules.
4. Error Handling Strategy Eksik

Production app için şart.

Eklenmeli:

## Error Handling

- All async operations must use try/catch.
- User-friendly fallback UI is mandatory.
- Audio recording failures must be handled gracefully.
- Network failures must not crash the app.
5. PWA Rules Eksik

PWA demişsin ama implementation contract yok.

Claude default basit setup yapabilir.

Eklenmeli:

## PWA Requirements

- Offline-first architecture.
- Cache exam content for offline access.
- User progress must persist locally.
- Service Worker required.
- Installable on Android/iOS/Desktop.
6. Accessibility (A11y) Eksik

Bu çok kritik.

Özellikle dil öğrenme platformunda.

Eklenmeli:

## Accessibility Requirements

- All interactive elements must be keyboard accessible.
- Proper ARIA labels are mandatory.
- Minimum contrast ratio WCAG AA.
- Audio controls must support screen readers.
7. Testing Strategy Eksik

Büyük eksik.

Claude test yazmazsa ileride teknik borç olur.

Eklenmeli:

## Testing Requirements

- Use Vitest + React Testing Library.
- Critical business logic must have unit tests.
- Zustand stores require test coverage.
- Audio timer logic must be tested.
8. Performance Constraints Eksik

Cyberpunk UI kolayca ağırlaşır.

Eklenmeli:

## Performance Requirements

- Minimize unnecessary re-renders.
- Use code splitting.
- Lazy load audio modules.
- Avoid large animation libraries.
- Lighthouse mobile performance target: 90+.
9. Security Rules Eksik

AI bazen kötü localStorage kullanımı yapar.

Eklenmeli:

## Security Rules

- Never store sensitive data in localStorage.
- Sanitize all dynamic HTML.
- Avoid eval or unsafe browser APIs.
- Validate all imported JSON content.
10. State Management Contract Eksik

Şu an Zustand kullanılıyor ama architecture yok.

Eklenmeli:

## Zustand Store Rules

- Keep stores flat and modular.
- Avoid business logic inside components.
- Use selectors to prevent unnecessary renders.
- Persist only UserProgress store.
- ExamContent store must remain immutable.
11. Audio Architecture Eksik (ÇOK KRİTİK)

Spreken senin core feature’ın.

Şu an çok yüzeysel yazılmış.

Claude ileride memory leak yaratabilir.

Eklenmeli:

## Audio System Requirements

- Use MediaRecorder API.
- Proper cleanup of audio streams is mandatory.
- Prevent microphone leaks on unmount.
- Recording state must survive UI re-renders.
- Waveform/timer updates should use requestAnimationFrame.
12. Navigation Architecture Eksik

SPA routing tanımlanmamış.

Eklenmeli:

## Routing

- Use React Router.
- Route-based code splitting is required.
- Preserve user progress between routes.
13. Design System Eksik

Şu an renkler var ama design token yok.

Eklenmeli:

## Design System

- Use Tailwind design tokens.
- Avoid inline styles.
- Use consistent spacing scale.
- Create reusable button/input/card variants.
14. Backend Hazırlığı Eksik

Şu an local-only gibi görünüyor.

Ama ileride auth/backend gelir.

Şimdiden şunu ekle:

## Future Backend Compatibility

- Architecture must remain backend-agnostic.
- All persistence logic should be abstracted behind services.
- Prepare for Supabase/Firebase integration.
15. AI Behavior Constraints Eksik (EN ÖNEMLİLERDEN)

Claude bazen:

gereksiz package ekler
overengineering yapar
context dışına çıkar

Bunu engelle:

## AI Development Constraints

- Do not introduce unnecessary dependencies.
- Prefer simple and maintainable solutions.
- Avoid overengineering.
- Follow existing architecture strictly.
- Never refactor unrelated code.
- Do not generate placeholder/mock business logic unless requested.

Bu bölüm aşırı önemli.

En Kritik Eksik

Bence en kritik eksik şu:

“Definition of Done”

Bunu koymazsan Claude yarım işler üretir.

Eklenmeli:

## Definition of Done

A task is complete only if:
- TypeScript passes with zero errors.
- ESLint passes.
- Components are responsive.
- i18n keys exist for all UI strings.
- No console errors/warnings.
- Dark mode compatibility verified.
- Mobile usability verified.
Ben Olsam Şunu da Eklerdim
Dependency Rules
## Dependency Policy

Preferred:
- Native browser APIs
- Lightweight libraries
- Headless UI approaches

Avoid unless necessary:
- Heavy UI frameworks
- Large animation libraries
- Complex state abstractions
